result.name: FreshTomato - Advanced Dark Edit
result.description:
Custom Colors For FreshTomato Firmware - Advanced Dark Theme

This Theme Is For People Running FreshTomato Firmware On There Router,
(I Haven't Tested It But May Work On Other Tomato Based Firmware - Use At Your Own Risk!),

Find the firmware here: https://freshtomato.org/

To Work Correctly You Must Set Theme UI To Advanced Dark In Router Settings First,
Administration > Admin Access > Web Admin > Theme UI: Advanced Dark
